item.title: Help in client
item.dc:creator: @N11 -N-
item.description:
@N11 wrote:

Go into your client folder and double click the “GUI” or “EGUI” file. There should be three lines of “127.0.0.1” with those quotations ["] around it. Just go and change the 127.0.0.1 to 5.114.189.83. (If that is your server IP).
